	(text "use JST headers for the analog headers to get the analog inputs onto the board	\n	- Consider each analog input to be one cable/connection in the JST connector\n	  (i.e. if we have a 4-pin JST: aInput1 (1), aInput2 (20, ... etc)\n	- get angled JST connectors"
